reviewText: HOW DO YOU ORDER THE SOUND TRACK OF THE MOVIE JUMPING THE BROOM

EVEN THOUGH I ALREADY HAD JUMPING THE BROOM DVD, I ORDERED THIS LIMITED EDITION SINCE I COULD NOT LOCATE THE SOUNDTRACK FOR THIS MOVIE WITHOUT ORDERING BOTH.  UNFORTUNATELY, THE SOUNDTRACK IS NOT THE SOUNDTRACK OF THE MOVIE - IT IS SOME GOSPEL MUSIC.

I CANNOT UNDERSTAND HOW I CANNOT ORDER SOUNDTRACK FOR THIS MOVIE.
